{"route":{"route":"/posts/3b8b96de/","outputPath":"posts/3b8b96de/index.html","kind":"post","title":"linux下intel&AMD双显卡切换","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"3b8b96de"}},"description":"使用 xrandr 显示可支持的显卡 输出类似以下内容 To be able to render GPU intensive applications by the more powerful discrete card use 或者 使用DRI PRIME为某个应用选择使用哪一张显卡,使用glxinfo可以查看正在使","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/linux下intel-AMD双显卡切换.md","route":"/posts/3b8b96de/","abbrlink":"3b8b96de","title":"linux下intel&AMD双显卡切换","date":"2018-09-08 19:02:47","updated":"2020-05-05 19:02:47","tags":["Linux","双显卡","AMD"],"categories":["Linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>使用<strong>xrandr</strong>显示可支持的显卡</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">xrandr</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --listproviders</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>输出类似以下内容</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">Providers:</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> number</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> :</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 2</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">Provider</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> 0:</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> id:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0x6b</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> cap:</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> 0x9,</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Source</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Output,</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Sink</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Offload</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> crtcs:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 3</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> outputs:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 7</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> associated</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> providers:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 1</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> name:modesetting</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">Provider</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> 1:</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> id:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0x41</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> cap:</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> 0x6,</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Sink</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Output,</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Source</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Offload</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> crtcs:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 2</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> outputs:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> associated</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> providers:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 1</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> name:OLAND</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> @</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> pci:0000:01:00.0</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>To be able to render GPU-intensive applications by the more powerful discrete card use</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">xrandr</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --setprovideroffloadsink</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 1</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>或者</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">xrandr</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --setprovideroffloadsink</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0x41</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0x6b</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>使用DRI_PRIME为某个应用选择使用哪一张显卡,使用glxinfo可以查看正在使用的显卡</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">DRI_PRIME</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">0</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> glxinfo</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\"> |</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> grep</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> \"OpenGL renderer\"</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">DRI_PRIME</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">1</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> glxinfo</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\"> |</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> grep</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> \"OpenGL renderer\"</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>如为steam启用独显</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">DRI_PRIME</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">1</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> steam</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>如果需要使用独显进行视频硬件播放,还需指定视频解码库,不然会乱码:<br>\n如AMD:</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">DRI_PRIME</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">1</span><span style=\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D\">            # for laptops with switchable graphics</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">LIBVA_DRIVER_NAME</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">r600</span><span style=\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D\"> # value depends on the driver, check /usr/lib/dri for possible options</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>使用mpv:</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">DRI_PRIME</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">1</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">  LIBVA_DRIVER_NAME</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">r600</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> mpv</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [...]</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>参考资料:<br>\n1.<a href=\"https://askubuntu.com/questions/1038271/intel-amd-hybrid-graphics-ubuntu-18-04\">Intel/AMD Hybrid graphics Ubuntu 18.04</a><br>\n2.<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/PRIME\">PRIME (简体中文)</a></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"3b8b96de","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}